Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:50.10,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}剎那間被誘惑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.26,0:21:54.66,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在欺騙的愛中沉淪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.48,0:22:01.60,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,5000)\an2}Get out……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:10.56,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望揮舞純真無邪之劍的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:16.19,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}盡情地讓疼痛貫穿我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.40,0:22:16.43,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an1}Just say you love me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.51,0:22:18.48,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}You know I've got a crush on you
